### Young workers ###

Until you're 18, you're classed as a young worker. You have different employment rights to child workers and adult workers.

### Part-time work

You can work part-time from 13, but you can only work a certain number of hours per week and do certain jobs.

### Entertainment work

You can work in entertainment, eg on TV or as a model, from any age. You'll need a performance licence from your local authority.
